z.start-R.start})}vo(i);var o=i.segments.length,c=0,h=[],v=[],p=[],g=[],T=[],P=[];for(r=0;r&lt;o;r+=1){var 0&amp;&amp;(T=T.concat({name:&quot;glyph_&quot;+r,type:&quot;USHORT&quot;,value:C.glyphId}))):c+=1,!t&amp;&amp;C.glyphIndex!==void 0&amp;&amp;(P=P.concat({name:&quot;cmap12Start_&quot;+r,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:C.start}),P=P.concat({name:&quot;cmap12End_&quot;+r,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:C.end}),P=P.concat({name:&quot;cmap12Glyph_&quot;+r,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:C.glyphIndex}))}if(i.segCountX2=(o-c)*2,i.searchRange=Math.pow(2,Math.floor(Math.log(o-c)/Math.log(2)))*2,i.entrySelector=Math.log(i.searchRange/2)/Math.log(2),i.rangeShift=i.segCountX2-i.searchRange,i.fields=i.fields.concat(h),i.fields.push({name:&quot;reservedPad&quot;,type:&quot;USHORT&quot;,value:0}),i.fields=i.fields.concat(v),i.fields=i.fields.concat(p),i.fields=i.fields.concat(g),i.fields=i.fields.concat(T),i.cmap4Length=14+h.length*2+2+v.length*2+p.length*2+g.length*2+T.length*2,!t){var O=16+P.length*4;i.cmap12Offset=12+2*2+4+i.cmap4Length,i.fields=i.fields.concat([{name:&quot;cmap12Format&quot;,type:&quot;USHORT&quot;,value:12},{name:&quot;cmap12Reserved&quot;,type:&quot;USHORT&quot;,value:0},{name:&quot;cmap12Length&quot;,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:O},{name:&quot;cmap12Language&quot;,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:0},{name:&quot;cmap12nGroups&quot;,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:P.length/3}]),i.fields=i.fields.concat(P)}return z.start-R.start})}vo(i);var o=i.segments.length,c=0,h=[],v=[],p=[],g=[],T=[],P=[];for(r=0;r&lt;o;r+=1){var 0&amp;&amp;(T=T.concat({name:&quot;glyph_&quot;+r,type:&quot;USHORT&quot;,value:C.glyphId}))):c+=1,!t&amp;&amp;C.glyphIndex!==void 0&amp;&amp;(P=P.concat({name:&quot;cmap12Start_&quot;+r,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:C.start}),P=P.concat({name:&quot;cmap12End_&quot;+r,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:C.end}),P=P.concat({name:&quot;cmap12Glyph_&quot;+r,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:C.glyphIndex}))}if(i.segCountX2=(o-c)*2,i.searchRange=Math.pow(2,Math.floor(Math.log(o-c)/Math.log(2)))*2,i.entrySelector=Math.log(i.searchRange/2)/Math.log(2),i.rangeShift=i.segCountX2-i.searchRange,i.fields=i.fields.concat(h),i.fields.push({name:&quot;reservedPad&quot;,type:&quot;USHORT&quot;,value:0}),i.fields=i.fields.concat(v),i.fields=i.fields.concat(p),i.fields=i.fields.concat(g),i.fields=i.fields.concat(T),i.cmap4Length=14+h.length*2+2+v.length*2+p.length*2+g.length*2+T.length*2,!t){var O=16+P.length*4;i.cmap12Offset=12+2*2+4+i.cmap4Length,i.fields=i.fields.concat([{name:&quot;cmap12Format&quot;,type:&quot;USHORT&quot;,value:12},{name:&quot;cmap12Reserved&quot;,type:&quot;USHORT&quot;,value:0},{name:&quot;cmap12Length&quot;,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:O},{name:&quot;cmap12Language&quot;,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:0},{name:&quot;cmap12nGroups&quot;,type:&quot;ULONG&quot;,value:P.length/3}]),i.fields=i.fields.concat(P)}return
